product.short-description:
The world has never seen a beauty quite like Brooke Shields. With effortless grace and an inner radiance, Brooke is as iconic as her career-defining roles ? from ethereal dream girl to castaway goddess, glamorous model-next-door to accomplished actress.
M?A?C partners with Ms. Shields to create a limited-edition colour collection of shades and finishes chosen by Brooke herself, inspired by her favourite looks for day and night ? easy, modern and beautiful.
Eye Shadow x 15 features fifteen shades in finishes from soft golden peach to duo chrome pink, frosted nudes and deep cocoas to shimmering olive, all in a convenient palette for creating an array of natural to smoky eyes. Veluxe Pearlfusion Shadow glides on in two coordinated colour waves. Be like Brooke by day with satin silver shimmer, violet and pink with gold pearl, or style an evening look based on her palette glimmering with cool beige, mid-tone grey, dark charcoal, blackened plum and brown.
Veluxe Brow Liner in Brunette and Clear Brow Set frame the face with modern, defined eyebrows, undeniably Brooke. Bronzing Powder in neutral tan enhances your skin tone, while Cremeblend Blush Duo combines coral pink with soft rose, polishing cheeks with blushing warmth.
Two lip looks express Brooke’s Gemini duality ? bright orange-red lustrously layered with matching Lipglass and a sophisticated shimmer of coral gloss complementing a rich, burgundy Lipstick. Play up the persona with a duo of corresponding Nail Lacquers in classic cream formulas.
This limited-edition Beauty Icon collection is made all the more special with Brooke’s signature embossed on light grey packaging with brilliant orange accents.
Our life-long romance with Brooke Shields is and always will be forever.
